description: APP是以ADAS为主的车联网产品，以硬件为ADAS载体主动提醒用户行车安全。ADAS（Advanced Driving Assistant System），即高级驾驶辅助系统，即在驾车过程中仍然以驾驶员为主导，APP 中的ADAS 起到提醒驾驶员、并在危急情况下反复提醒
en_description: APP is based on the ADAS car networking products, with the hardware as a ADAS carrier to remind users of driving safety. ADAS (Advanced Driving System Assistant), that is, advanced driver assistance system, that is still in the driver's driving process, APP in the ADAS to remind the driver, and in a critical situation repeatedly reminded
